{"type":"message","id":"89471bc4","parentId":"04234f61","timestamp":"2026-04-15T09:59:21.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me provide a concise summary to Lead.","thinkingSignature":"3ecf540cf0bef36f095d36f17ad44629e4e1b73cc2e7a0a69452da62d86190ba"},{"type":"text","text":"**Decision: Throttle heartbeat → 15 min (from 5 min)**\n\nWhy not disable? Monitoring still needed for agent failures + session changes. On-demand-only loses change detection.\n\nWhy 15 min specifically? 5 min = ~288 sessions/day. 10 min = ~144. 15 min = ~96. Best cost/benefit.\n\n| What | Change |\n|---|---|\n| cron `6f3323ef` (DTLX/QLHV) | `everyMs`: 300000 → 900000 |\n| cron `ed2d0b5d` (AHV Works) | `everyMs`: 300000 → 900000 |\n| HEARTBEAT.md | All refs updated (5p → 15p) |\n| Committed | `bfe6e8e` |\n\nSessions/day estimate: **~288 → ~96 (67% reduction)**. Registry bloat resolved without losing monitoring capability.\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":135,"output":216,"cacheRead":29014,"cacheWrite":593,"totalTokens":29958,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776247155330,"responseId":"062e947454cdd8baa8a5aa47f069cfa6"}}
