{"type":"message","id":"4a0b6f03","parentId":"b9758ad7","timestamp":"2026-04-15T10:32:11.447Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_z9x59vvufg56_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n# HEARTBEAT.md — Ecosystem Sentinel\\n\\n_Runs every ~10 minutes. Monitors pipeline health + broadcasts agent presence._\\n\\n---\\n\\n## ⏰ Timed Triggers\\n\\n### Every ~10 min — Pipeline Health Sweep\\n\\n```\\n1. sessions_list → count active sessions\\n2. subagents → check for failed/stuck agents\\n3. If any agent FAILED:\\n     → Report to Khuowgn immediately\\n     → sessions_send FEEDBACK.md to stalled agent\\n4. If pipeline healthy:\\n     → Stay silent (no noise to Khuowgn)\\n```\\n\\n### Every ~15 min — Change Detection (Telegram)\\n\\n```\\n1. sessions_list → get all active sessions\\n2. Read memory/heartbeat-state.json → compare with last known state\\n3. If NO CHANGE since last report:\\n     → Stay SILENT. Exit quietly. No message sent.\\n4. If CHANGE detected (new session, died, failed, blocker):\\n     → Compose change report → s\\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n# HEARTBEAT.md — Ecosystem Sentinel\n\n_Runs every ~10 minutes. Monitors pipeline health + broadcasts agent presence._\n\n---\n\n## ⏰ Timed Triggers\n\n### Every ~10 min — Pipeline Health Sweep\n\n```\n1. sessions_list → count active sessions\n2. subagents → check for failed/stuck agents\n3. If any agent FAILED:\n     → Report to Khuowgn immediately\n     → sessions_send FEEDBACK.md to stalled agent\n4. If pipeline healthy:\n     → Stay silent (no noise to Khuowgn)\n```\n\n### Every ~15 min — Change Detection (Telegram)\n\n```\n1. sessions_list → get all active sessions\n2. Read memory/heartbeat-state.json → compare with last known state\n3. If NO CHANGE since last report:\n     → Stay SILENT. Exit quietly. No message sent.\n4. If CHANGE detected (new session, died, failed, blocker):\n     → Compose change report → s\n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776249131430}}
