{"type":"message","id":"b63a2bab","parentId":"21b75089","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:36:50.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both BE and FE build successfully. Now let me summarize for the Lead.","thinkingSignature":"eec62c3ffc6ff70864f8f8d791430502f19992fa3d2d82d16fa60ce48568c94f"},{"type":"text","text":"Cả 2 build ✅. Tổng kết:\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Setup Complete\n\n| | BE | FE |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Sync** | develop synced (98 commits) | develop synced (59 commits + 9 local) |\n| **Conflicts** | Auto-resolved | Resolved (accepted remote) |\n| **Branch** | `feat/notification-channel` | `feat/notification-channel` |\n| **Build** | ✅ tsc + tsc-alias | ✅ Next.js build |\n\n**Hai nhánh `feat/notification-channel` đã sẵn sàng trên cả BE và FE.**\n\nGhi chú:\n- Nhánh mới từ `origin/develop` (code mới nhất)\n- **KHÔNG push** — chỉ commit local\n- Muốn tạo MR → báo Lead review\n\nBây giờ cần thêm chi tiết yêu cầu:\n- **SMS**: dùng provider nào (VNPT, Viettel, Twilio, ...)?\n- **Zalo**: Zalo OA API? Notifications gửi từ OA nào?\n- **App notification**: Push notification (FCM) hay in-app notification?\n- **Trigger**: Khi nào thì gửi? (đăng ký, nhắc học phí, kết quả thi, ...?)\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":179,"output":330,"cacheRead":43915,"cacheWrite":199,"totalTokens":44623,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776285401521,"responseId":"062f29da88396cae935e46d8682f98a4"}}
