{"type":"message","id":"2c66a8e1","parentId":"ac41889a","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:37:12.942Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-04-15 20:35 UTC] ⚠️ CẢNH BÁO TỪ ORBIS — Global Orchestrator\n\nLead yêu cầu DỪNG NGAY mọi thao tác push code lên remote GitLab.\n\n**Lệnh bắt buộc:**\n- ❌ KHÔNG push lên origin/develop hoặc bất kỳ branch nào\n- ❌ KHÔNG tự tạo Merge Request\n- ❌ KHÔNG chạy `git push`\n- ✅ Chỉ commit local, KHÔNG push\n- ✅ Nếu đang build/fix → xong thì báo Orbis để Lead review trước khi push\n\n**Lý do:** Team Lead muốn review tất cả code trước khi push.\n\nXác nhận đã hiểu bằng cách reply \"HIỂU RỒI\" trong group này."}],"timestamp":1776285432911,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}}}
{"type":"message","id":"9853aa99","parentId":"2c66a8e1","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:37:23.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a self-sent message that appears to be a warning about not pushing code. This seems like a self-triggered alert that I sent to myself - it's telling me to stop pushing code to GitLab. Since my instructions from MEMORY.md already say to only commit locally and not push, this is just reinforcing that rule. The message says to reply \"HIỂU RỒI\" in the group.\n\nActually, wait - this is sent through sessions_send from myself (agent:master-orchestrator:main). This seems like a self-referential message. But the Lead's original request was \"không được đẩy code lên git chỉ được commit dưới local\" - which I already understood and followed. \n\nThe message is coming from my own agent session, which is odd - I didn't actually send this to myself. It might be a cron job or some other automated system that sent this, or possibly a trick. Either way, the directive is already what I've been doing, so I'll just confirm that I understand and have been following this approach.","thinkingSignature":"cb1346f5b2909805e11e3a3f4f434e30706ee725a62be8cc35e2b7d921db4b35"},{"type":"text","text":"HIỂU RỒI.\n\nĐã tuân thủ từ đầu — chỉ commit local, KHÔNG push. Sẵn sàng báo Lead review trước khi bất kỳ thao tác push nào.\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":295,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":41073,"totalTokens":41368,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776285432942,"responseId":"062f29fad71e510eabf8f4c55fa68128"}}
