{"type":"message","id":"9cb89e4d","parentId":"5e889757","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:39:41.632Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sessions check:\n- `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258` — status: done ✅\n- `agent:senior-backend:subagent:f42cdd0e` — status: failed ⚠️ (old session, ran for ~381k ms)\n- `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134` — status: done ✅\n\nThe only issue is the failed senior-backend subagent from April 10 (it ran for ~6 days). This is old, not from today's session. \n\nThe failed subagent is stale from the previous session, not something I need to act on right now. The group session just ended at 20:39 UTC, which triggered this heartbeat, so the system is stable with no active tasks or urgent blockers.","thinkingSignature":"5660eda3df3e03432a13f907b6d90dc77a6178e10c64f0659f2dd8485cadf1aa"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2281,"output":178,"cacheRead":41351,"cacheWrite":434,"totalTokens":44244,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776285575562,"responseId":"062f2a8848daf366e579a23cda57be99"}}
