{"type":"message","id":"2b6e23f0","parentId":"a8d14712","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:40:22.035Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vxmgm94op3fj_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"(no notification env vars yet)\n---\nimport { apiClient } from './api';\n\nexport interface Notification {\n  _id: string;\n  id?: string;\n  receive_id: string;\n  receive_type: 'user' | 'student' | 'teacher';\n  category?: 'notif' | 'system';\n  title: string;\n  body: string;\n  content: string; // From new model\n  is_read: boolean;\n  status: 'unread' | 'read'; // From new model\n  channel: 'in_app' | 'zalo' | 'sms' | 'email';\n  data?: any;\n  created_at: string;\n  createdAt: string; // From new model\n  updated_at: string;\n  updatedAt: string;\n}\n\nexport const getNotifications = async (userId: string, page = 1, limit = 20) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/user/${userId}?page=${page}&limit=${limit}`);\n};\n\nexport const markAsRead = async (id: string, userId?: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/${id}/read${userId ? `?userId=${userId}` : ''}`, {\n    method: 'PATCH'\n  });\n};"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":60,"aggregated":"(no notification env vars yet)\n---\nimport { apiClient } from './api';\n\nexport interface Notification {\n  _id: string;\n  id?: string;\n  receive_id: string;\n  receive_type: 'user' | 'student' | 'teacher';\n  category?: 'notif' | 'system';\n  title: string;\n  body: string;\n  content: string; // From new model\n  is_read: boolean;\n  status: 'unread' | 'read'; // From new model\n  channel: 'in_app' | 'zalo' | 'sms' | 'email';\n  data?: any;\n  created_at: string;\n  createdAt: string; // From new model\n  updated_at: string;\n  updatedAt: string;\n}\n\nexport const getNotifications = async (userId: string, page = 1, limit = 20) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/user/${userId}?page=${page}&limit=${limit}`);\n};\n\nexport const markAsRead = async (id: string, userId?: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/${id}/read${userId ? `?userId=${userId}` : ''}`, {\n    method: 'PATCH'\n  });\n};","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776285621998}}
{"type":"message","id":"225c42dc","parentId":"2b6e23f0","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:40:35.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. The system already has:\n- BE: notification models (notifyContent, notifyConfig, notify, notifyUser)\n- BE: NotifyService and NotifyController\n- BE: Routes for notifications\n- FE: NotificationService with `channel: 'in_app' | 'zalo' | 'sms' | 'email'`\n\nWhat's missing:\n1. **SMS (Twilio)** - Need to install twilio SDK, add env vars, create SMS sender\n2. **Zalo OA Push** - Need Zalo API integration\n3. **Push Notification** - Need FCM/WebSocket for in-app real-time\n\n\n4. **Channel router** - A notification service that orchestrates sending across different channels\n5. **Announcement CRUD** - Need to add endpoints for managing announcements in the BE\n\nFor the SMS implementation, I'll need to install the Twilio SDK, configure the necessary credentials, and set up a dedicated SMS sender class. For Zalo, I'm thinking about how to integrate their API for sending messages.\n\nFor in-app push notifications, I could go with Firebase Cloud Messaging for mobile apps or set up WebSocket/SSE for real-time delivery. I'm planning to tackle this in phases: first the SMS channel through Twilio, then the Zalo OA push notifications, and finally the in-app push notification infrastructure.\n\nNow I need to gather the necessary API credentials from the Lead—specifically the Twilio SID, auth token, and phone numbers, plus the Zalo OA ID, secret key, and access token for the ZNS messages.","thinkingSignature":"cd092654e90329035fd70673a71183d87ce859ec2f03eeae85c453b0e4bfc722"},{"type":"text","text":"Đã nắm rõ hệ thống. Đây là bức tranh hiện tại:\n\n### Hệ thống hiện có\n| Thành phần | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|\n| BE: notifyContent/notifyConfig/notify model | ✅ Có sẵn |\n| BE: NotifyService + Controller | ✅ Có sẵn |\n| BE: Routes `/notifications/*` | ✅ Có sẵn |\n| FE: notificationService + channel types | ✅ Có sẵn (`in_app`, `zalo`, `sms`, `email`) |\n| Twilio / Zalo OA / FCM | ❌ Chưa tích hợp |\n\n### Cần cung cấp\n\nĐể implement đúng, tôi cần từ Lead:\n\n**Twilio SMS:**\n- `TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID` = ?\n- `TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN` = ?\n- `TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER` = (số gửi SMS)\n\n**Zalo OA:**\n- `ZALO_APP_ID` = ?\n- `ZALO_APP_SECRET` = ?\n- `ZALO_OA_ID` = ?\n\n**Push Notification (in-app):**\n- Dùng Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) hay tự build WebSocket?\n- Hoặc Lead muốn notification chỉ lưu DB + hiển thị trong app (không cần real-time push)?\n\n**Trigger scenarios** — muốn gửi notification khi nào?\n- Khi học viên đăng ký khóa học\n- Nhắc học phí\n- Kết quả thi\n- Thông báo từ admin (thủ công)\n- Tất cả các trường hợp trên?\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":401,"output":746,"cacheRead":53071,"cacheWrite":709,"totalTokens":54927,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776285622041,"responseId":"062f2ab7af740478e6d6a93296f8e1c1"}}
