{"type":"message","id":"17d26e57","parentId":"a823ddba","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:43:24.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants me to:\n1. Proceed without the API keys for now (use placeholder .env for all cases) - they'll send the keys later\n2. After finishing notification channels, checkout a new branch for the remaining features\n3. Survey remaining incomplete features\n4. Complete them\n5. Write Swagger API docs\n6. Clean code + optimize\n\nLet me start implementing the notification channels (SMS via Twilio, Zalo OA, and in-app) using placeholder configs. I'll create the integration services, update the notify service, and set up .env.example with all the needed keys.\n\nLet me think about the architecture:\n\n1. **BE - Channel Provider Services** (new files):\n   - `src/infrastructure/channels/twilio-sms.service.ts` - Twilio SMS\n   - `src/infrastructure/channels/zalo-oa.service.ts` - Zalo OA\n   - `src/infrastructure/channels/fcm-push.service.ts` - Firebase/FCM for in-app push\n   - `src/infrastructure/channels/notification-channel.service.ts` - Unified dispatcher\n\n2. **BE - NotifyService update**:\n   - Add channel dispatch when creating notification\n   - Read channel config from NotifyConfigs collection\n\n3. **BE - .env.example update**:\n   - Add all channel API keys (placeholders)\n\n4. **FE - Notification page**:\n   - Add channel selector for sending notifications\n   - Display channel status\n\nNow I'll start building these services with placeholder configs for Twilio, Zalo, and FCM, update the notify service to route notifications through the appropriate channels, and add the channel fields to the notification interface. I need to create the channel provider services for SMS, Zalo, and FCM, then build a unified dispatcher that routes notifications based on the selected channel. After updating the NotifyService and .env configuration, I'll document the Swagger API endpoints and clean up the codebase before implementing any remaining features. I also need to survey what's already completed versus what's still outstanding.","thinkingSignature":"f706bddfd4403933f7224149531c1b63b3b37ec75fffaf025e94539872139084"},{"type":"text","text":"Rõ rồi — proceed without keys, dùng placeholder `.env.example`, survey features còn thiếu, clean code + optimize, viết Swagger. Tôi triển khai ngay.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_le8x2tqwvj9o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/routes/ -name \"*.ts\" | sort | while read f; do\n  name=$(basename \"$f\" .ts)\n  count=$(grep -c \"router\\.\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null || echo 0)\n  echo \"$name: $count routes\"\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":116,"output":572,"cacheRead":53612,"cacheWrite":1337,"totalTokens":55637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776285788167,"responseId":"062f2b5e37642bf533b8389e22b91997"}}
