{"type":"message","id":"d7b50e42","parentId":"7250a860","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:44:47.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"FE has these pages: courses, dashboard, exam-batches, graduation-exam, help, notifications, practice, profile, progress, sat-hach, schedules, settings, students, tuition.\n\nLet me now write the comprehensive swagger.json and save it. I'll also check what notification FE components look like to see if they need channel support.\n\nLet me focus on the swagger first - I'll write a comprehensive one covering all routes with proper schemas.","thinkingSignature":"e0eba897086598e9568c9f4de5ac686130ec6dce7569f112794edafecc5ee026"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p9w8zig2fpvd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/notificationService.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":211,"output":141,"cacheRead":61651,"cacheWrite":1393,"totalTokens":63396,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776285881453,"responseId":"062f2bbb0eff5a679894f1d13046e2c0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"92efba14","parentId":"d7b50e42","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:44:47.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p9w8zig2fpvd_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { apiClient } from './api';\n\nexport interface Notification {\n  _id: string;\n  id?: string;\n  receive_id: string;\n  receive_type: 'user' | 'student' | 'teacher';\n  category?: 'notif' | 'system';\n  title: string;\n  body: string;\n  content: string; // From new model\n  is_read: boolean;\n  status: 'unread' | 'read'; // From new model\n  channel: 'in_app' | 'zalo' | 'sms' | 'email';\n  data?: any;\n  created_at: string;\n  createdAt: string; // From new model\n  updated_at: string;\n  updatedAt: string;\n}\n\nexport const getNotifications = async (userId: string, page = 1, limit = 20) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/user/${userId}?page=${page}&limit=${limit}`);\n};\n\nexport const markAsRead = async (id: string, userId?: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/${id}/read${userId ? `?userId=${userId}` : ''}`, {\n    method: 'PATCH'\n  });\n};\n\nexport const markAllNotificationsAsRead = async (userId: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/user/${userId}/read-all`, {\n    method: 'PATCH'\n  });\n};\n\nexport const deleteNotification = async (id: string, userId?: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/${id}${userId ? `?userId=${userId}` : ''}`, {\n    method: 'DELETE'\n  });\n};"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":23,"aggregated":"import { apiClient } from './api';\n\nexport interface Notification {\n  _id: string;\n  id?: string;\n  receive_id: string;\n  receive_type: 'user' | 'student' | 'teacher';\n  category?: 'notif' | 'system';\n  title: string;\n  body: string;\n  content: string; // From new model\n  is_read: boolean;\n  status: 'unread' | 'read'; // From new model\n  channel: 'in_app' | 'zalo' | 'sms' | 'email';\n  data?: any;\n  created_at: string;\n  createdAt: string; // From new model\n  updated_at: string;\n  updatedAt: string;\n}\n\nexport const getNotifications = async (userId: string, page = 1, limit = 20) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/user/${userId}?page=${page}&limit=${limit}`);\n};\n\nexport const markAsRead = async (id: string, userId?: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/${id}/read${userId ? `?userId=${userId}` : ''}`, {\n    method: 'PATCH'\n  });\n};\n\nexport const markAllNotificationsAsRead = async (userId: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/user/${userId}/read-all`, {\n    method: 'PATCH'\n  });\n};\n\nexport const deleteNotification = async (id: string, userId?: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/notifications/${id}${userId ? `?userId=${userId}` : ''}`, {\n    method: 'DELETE'\n  });\n};","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776285887555}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f0482a7","parentId":"92efba14","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:47:20.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me write the comprehensive swagger.json. I'll include all routes from all controllers with proper schemas.\n\nThis is a large file, let me write it carefully.","thinkingSignature":"df244fc701a001ff92c76a0fbc8f7a11dc32cf94ef42f41f3f74f863957dbbbc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cloy51jn049n_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/docs/swagger.json","content":"{\n  \"openapi\": \"3.0.3\",\n  \"info\": {\n    \"title\": \"AHV QLHV - Hệ thống Quản lý Đào tạo Lái xe\",\n    \"description\": \"## Mô tả\\nHệ thống API RESTful cho module Quản lý Học viên Đào tạo Lái xe (QLHV).\\n\\n**Base URL:** `/api/v1`\\n\\n**Authentication:** Bearer Token (JWT)\\n\\n## Channels\\nHệ thống hỗ trợ 4 kênh thông báo:\\n- `in_app` — Thông báo trong ứng dụng\\n- `sms` — Tin nhắn SMS qua Twilio\\n- `zalo` — Tin nhắn Zalo OA\\n- `fcm` — Push notification qua Firebase Cloud Messaging\\n\\n## Pagination\\nTất cả các API list đều hỗ trợ:\\n- `page` (default: 1)\\n- `limit` (default: 20, max: 100)\\n\\n## Response Format\\n```json\\n{ \\\"success\\\": true, \\\"data\\\": {...}, \\\"meta\\\": { \\\"total\\\": N, \\\"page\\\": 1, \\\"limit\\\": 20, \\\"total_pages\\\": 1 } }\\n```\",\n    \"version\": \"1.2.0\",\n    \"contact\": {\n      \"name\": \"AHV Dev Team\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"servers\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"/api/v1\",\n      \"description\": \"Development / Production\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"tags\": [\n    { \"name\": \"Auth\", \"description\": \"Xác thực & quản lý phiên\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Student\", \"description\": \"Quản lý học viên\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Course\", \"description\": \"Quản lý khóa học\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Exam\", \"description\": \"Quản lý kỳ thi\" },\n    { \"name\": \"ExamBatch\", \"description\": \"Quản lý đợt thi\" },\n    { \"name\": \"ExamSchedule\", \"description\": \"Lịch thi\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Lesson\", \"description\": \"Quản lý buổi học\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Payment\", \"description\": \"Quản lý học phí & thanh toán\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Dashboard\", \"description\": \"Thống kê tổng quan\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Notification\", \"description\": \"Thông báo (in-app, SMS, Zalo, FCM)\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Announcement\", \"description\": \"Thông báo hệ thống từ Admin\" },\n    { \"name\": \"City\", \"description\": \"Quản lý Tỉnh/Thành phố\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Stadium\", \"description\": \"Quản lý Sân tập\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Settings\", \"description\": \"Cấu hình hệ thống\" },\n    { \"name\": \"VipQr\", \"description\": \"QR VIP\" },\n    { \"name\": \"LicenseCategory\", \"description\": \"Loại bằng lái\" },\n    { \"name\": \"DAT\", \"description\": \"Đào tạo thực hành\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Data\", \"description\": \"Export / Import dữ liệu\" }\n  ],\n  \"components\": {\n    \"securitySchemes\": {\n      \"BearerAuth\": {\n        \"type\": \"http\",\n        \"scheme\": \"bearer\",\n        \"bearerFormat\": \"JWT\",\n        \"description\": \"JWT token từ endpoint `/auth/login`\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"schemas\": {\n      \"Error\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"success\": { \"type\": \"boolean\", \"example\": false },\n          \"message\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Unauthorized\" },\n          \"errors\": { \"type\": \"array\", \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Success\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"success\": { \"type\": \"boolean\", \"example\": true },\n          \"data\": { \"type\": \"object\" },\n          \"meta\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/PaginationMeta\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"PaginationMeta\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"total\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 100 },\n          \"page\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 1 },\n          \"limit\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 20 },\n          \"total_pages\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 5 }\n        }\n      },\n      \"PaginationQuery\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"page\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"default\": 1, \"description\": \"Trang hiện tại\" },\n          \"limit\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"default\": 20, \"description\": \"Số bản ghi/trang\" }\n        },\n        \"in\": \"query\"\n      },\n      \"Student\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"first_name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Nguyễn Văn\" },\n          \"last_name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"An\" },\n          \"phone\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"0909123456\" },\n          \"email\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"an@example.com\" },\n          \"identity_card\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"079201234567\" },\n          \"address\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"123 Đường ABC, Quận 1, TP.HCM\" },\n          \"license_category\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"B2\" },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"dang_hoc\", \"da_tot_nghiep\", \"chua_dong_hoc_phi\"] },\n          \"created_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Course\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Khóa B2 Cơ bản\" },\n          \"vehicle_type\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"B2\" },\n          \"duration_hours\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 120 },\n          \"price\": { \"type\": \"number\", \"example\": 4500000 },\n          \"description\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"active\", \"inactive\"] },\n          \"created_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Exam\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Kỳ thi sát hạch B2 - Đợt 1\" },\n          \"exam_date\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" },\n          \"location\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Sân thi Sài Gòn\" },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"scheduled\", \"ongoing\", \"completed\", \"cancelled\"] },\n          \"student_count\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 45 },\n          \"created_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"ExamBatch\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Đợt thi B2 tháng 4/2026\" },\n          \"exam_date\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date\" },\n          \"location\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"slot_count\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 50 },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"open\", \"closed\", \"completed\"] },\n          \"created_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"ExamSchedule\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"exam_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"student_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"scheduled_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" },\n          \"location\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"scheduled\", \"present\", \"absent\", \"passed\", \"failed\"] },\n          \"result_note\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Lesson\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"course_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"teacher_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"student_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"title\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Buổi 1 - Làm quen xe\" },\n          \"scheduled_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" },\n          \"duration_minutes\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 90 },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"scheduled\", \"in_progress\", \"completed\", \"cancelled\"] },\n          \"location\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"note\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Payment\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"student_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"amount\": { \"type\": \"number\", \"example\": 1500000 },\n          \"payment_date\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" },\n          \"method\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"cash\", \"bank_transfer\", \"momo\", \"zalopay\", \"vnpay\"] },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"pending\", \"completed\", \"failed\", \"refunded\"] },\n          \"note\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"collector_name\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Notification\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"receive_id\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"User/Student ID nhận thông báo\" },\n          \"title\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Nhắc học phí\" },\n          \"body\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Bạn còn nợ 2.000.000đ học phí\" },\n          \"channel\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"in_app\", \"sms\", \"zalo\", \"fcm\"], \"description\": \"Kênh gửi thông báo\" },\n          \"is_read\": { \"type\": \"boolean\" },\n          \"data\": { \"type\": \"object\", \"description\": \"Metadata bổ sung\" },\n          \"created_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Announcement\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"title\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Thông báo nghỉ lễ\" },\n          \"content\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Hệ thống nghỉ lễ 30/4 - 1/5\" },\n          \"target_group\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"ALL\", \"STUDENT\", \"TEACHER\", \"STAFF\"], \"example\": \"ALL\" },\n          \"channels\": { \"type\": \"array\", \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"in_app\", \"sms\", \"zalo\", \"fcm\"] } },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"SENT\", \"SCHEDULED\", \"DRAFT\", \"CANCELLED\"] },\n          \"scheduled_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" },\n          \"created_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"City\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"TP. Hồ Chí Minh\" },\n          \"code\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"79\" },\n          \"region\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"South\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"Stadium\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Sân tập lái Nguyễn Kiệm\" },\n          \"address\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"city_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"vehicle_types\": { \"type\": \"array\", \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"example\": [\"B1\", \"B2\", \"C\"] },\n          \"slot_count\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 10 },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"active\", \"inactive\"] }\n        }\n      },\n      \"LicenseCategory\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"code\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"B2\" },\n          \"name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Hạng B2 - Ô tô 4-9 chỗ\" },\n          \"description\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"theory_hours\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n          \"practice_hours\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n          \"min_age\": { \"type\": \"integer\", \"example\": 18 },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"active\", \"inactive\"] }\n        }\n      },\n      \"LoginRequest\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"username\", \"password\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"username\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"admin@gmail.com\" },\n          \"password\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Password123@\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"RegisterRequest\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"username\", \"password\", \"email\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"username\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"password\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"email\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"user@example.com\" },\n          \"first_name\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"last_name\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"phone\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"role\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"admin\", \"teacher\", \"staff\", \"student\"] }\n        }\n      },\n      \"LoginResponse\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"success\": { \"type\": \"boolean\" },\n          \"data\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"token\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n              \"user\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/User\" }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"User\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"username\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"email\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"role\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"admin\", \"teacher\", \"staff\", \"student\"] },\n          \"first_name\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"last_name\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"phone\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"DashboardStats\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"total_students\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n          \"total_courses\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n          \"total_exams\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n          \"total_revenue\": { \"type\": \"number\" },\n          \"monthly_stats\": {\n            \"type\": \"array\",\n            \"items\": {\n              \"type\": \"object\",\n              \"properties\": {\n                \"month\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n                \"students\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n                \"revenue\": { \"type\": \"number\" }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"DATAnalytics\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"total_sessions\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n          \"total_hours\": { \"type\": \"number\" },\n          \"by_student\": {\n            \"type\": \"array\",\n            \"items\": {\n              \"type\": \"object\",\n              \"properties\": {\n                \"student_id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n                \"sessions_count\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n                \"total_hours\": { \"type\": \"number\" }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"VipQrConfig\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"id\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"vip_code\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"qr_data\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"discount_percent\": { \"type\": \"number\", \"example\": 10 },\n          \"active\": { \"type\": \"boolean\" },\n          \"expires_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"SendNotificationRequest\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"receive_id\", \"title\", \"body\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"receive_id\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"User/Student ID nhận notification\" },\n          \"title\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Thông báo\" },\n          \"body\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Nội dung thông báo\" },\n          \"channel\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"in_app\", \"sms\", \"zalo\", \"fcm\"], \"default\": \"in_app\", \"description\": \"Kênh gửi\" },\n          \"data\": { \"type\": \"object\", \"description\": \"Metadata tùy chỉnh\" }\n        }\n      },\n      \"CreateAnnouncementRequest\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"title\", \"content\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"title\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Thông báo quan trọng\" },\n          \"content\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"example\": \"Nội dung thông báo\" },\n          \"target_group\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"ALL\", \"STUDENT\", \"TEACHER\", \"STAFF\"], \"default\": \"ALL\" },\n          \"channels\": {\n            \"type\": \"array\",\n            \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"in_app\", \"sms\", \"zalo\", \"fcm\"] },\n            \"example\": [\"in_app\", \"zalo\"]\n          },\n          \"status\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"SENT\", \"SCHEDULED\", \"DRAFT\"], \"default\": \"SENT\" },\n          \"scheduled_at\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"date-time\", \"description\": \"Thời gian gửi (nếu SCHEDULED)\" }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"paths\": {\n    \"/auth/login\": {\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Auth\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Đăng nhập\",\n        \"description\": \"Xác thực người dùng và nhận JWT token.\",\n        \"requestBody\": {\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"content\": {\n            \"application/json\": {\n              \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/LoginRequest\" }\n            }\n          }\n        },\n        \"responses\": {\n          \"200\": { \"description\": \"Đăng nhập thành công\", \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/LoginResponse\" } } } },\n          \"401\": { \"description\": \"Sai tài khoản/mật khẩu\", \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Error\" } } } }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/auth/register\": {\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Auth\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Đăng ký tài khoản mới\",\n        \"requestBody\": {\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/RegisterRequest\" } } }\n        },\n        \"responses\": {\n          \"201\": { \"description\": \"Đăng ký thành công\" },\n          \"400\": { \"description\": \"Dữ liệu không hợp lệ\", \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Error\" } } } }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/auth/me\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Auth\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Lấy thông tin người dùng hiện tại\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"responses\": {\n          \"200\": { \"description\": \"Thông tin user\", \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": { \"success\": { \"type\": \"boolean\" }, \"data\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/User\" } } } } } },\n          \"401\": { \"description\": \"Chưa đăng nhập\", \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Error\" } } } }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/auth/me\": {\n      \"put\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Auth\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Cập nhật thông tin người dùng hiện tại\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"requestBody\": {\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": { \"first_name\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"last_name\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"phone\": { \"type\": \"string\" } } } } }\n        },\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Cập nhật thành công\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/auth/change-password\": {\n      \"patch\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Auth\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Đổi mật khẩu\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"requestBody\": {\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"type\": \"object\", \"required\": [\"oldPassword\", \"newPassword\"], \"properties\": { \"oldPassword\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"newPassword\": { \"type\": \"string\" } } } } }\n        },\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Đổi mật khẩu thành công\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/auth/logout\": {\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Auth\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Đăng xuất\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Đăng xuất thành công\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/auth/refresh-token\": {\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Auth\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Làm mới JWT token\",\n        \"description\": \"Dùng refresh token để lấy token mới khi token cũ sắp hết hạn.\",\n        \"requestBody\": {\n          \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": { \"refreshToken\": { \"type\": \"string\" } } } } }\n        },\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Token mới\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/students\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Danh sách học viên\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [\n          { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/PaginationQuery\" },\n          { \"name\": \"search\", \"in\": \"query\", \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"description\": \"Tìm kiếm theo tên, SĐT, email\" },\n          { \"name\": \"status\", \"in\": \"query\", \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"description\": \"Filter theo trạng thái\" },\n          { \"name\": \"license_category\", \"in\": \"query\", \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"description\": \"Filter theo loại bằng\" }\n        ],\n        \"responses\": {\n          \"200\": { \"description\": \"Danh sách học viên\", \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Success\" } } } }\n        }\n      },\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Tạo học viên mới\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"requestBody\": {\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Student\" } } }\n        },\n        \"responses\": { \"201\": { \"description\": \"Tạo thành công\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/students/export\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Export danh sách học viên ra Excel\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [\n          { \"name\": \"search\", \"in\": \"query\", \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } },\n          { \"name\": \"status\", \"in\": \"query\", \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }\n        ],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"File Excel (.xlsx)\", \"content\": { \"application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet\": {} } } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/students/{id}\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Chi tiết học viên\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Chi tiết học viên\" } }\n      },\n      \"put\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Cập nhật học viên\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"requestBody\": { \"required\": true, \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Student\" } } } },\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Cập nhật thành công\" } }\n      },\n      \"delete\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Xóa học viên\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Xóa thành công\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/students/{id}/history\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Lịch sử học viên\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Lịch sử học tập\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/students/license-categories\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Danh sách loại bằng của học viên\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Danh sách license categories\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/students/import\": {\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Import học viên từ Excel\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"requestBody\": {\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"content\": { \"multipart/form-data\": { \"schema\": { \"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": { \"file\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"binary\", \"description\": \"File Excel (.xlsx)\" } } } } }\n        },\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Import thành công, trả về số bản ghi đã tạo/cập nhật\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/students/template\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Student\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Download template import học viên\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"File Excel template\", \"content\": { \"application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet\": {} } } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/courses\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Course\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Danh sách khóa học\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [\n          { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/PaginationQuery\" },\n          { \"name\": \"vehicle_type\", \"in\": \"query\", \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" }, \"description\": \"Filter theo loại xe (B1, B2, C...)\" }\n        ],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Danh sách khóa học\" } }\n      },\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Course\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Tạo khóa học mới\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"requestBody\": { \"required\": true, \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Course\" } } } },\n        \"responses\": { \"201\": { \"description\": \"Tạo thành công\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/courses/{id}\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Course\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Chi tiết khóa học\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Chi tiết khóa học\" } }\n      },\n      \"put\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Course\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Cập nhật khóa học\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"requestBody\": { \"required\": true, \"content\": { \"application/json\": { \"schema\": { \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/Course\" } } } },\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Cập nhật thành công\" } }\n      },\n      \"delete\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Course\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Xóa khóa học\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Xóa thành công\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/courses/{id}/unassigned-students\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Course\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Học viên chưa được gán vào khóa học\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"type\": \"string\" } }],\n        \"responses\": { \"200\": { \"description\": \"Danh sách học viên chưa gán\" } }\n      }\n    },\n    \"/courses/{id}/students\": {\n      \"post\": {\n        \"tags\": [\"Course\"],\n        \"summary\": \"Gán học viên vào khóa học\",\n        \"security\": [{ \"BearerAuth\": [] }],\n        \"parameters\": [{ \"name\": \"id\", \"in\": \"path\", \"required\": true, \"schema\": { \"ty