ame\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be && git commit -m \\\"feat(notification): add Twilio SMS, Zalo OA, and FCM push channel dispatchers\\\" 2>&1\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1776286094592,\n      \"responseId\": \"062f2c8e3c43edc2e7bb10f5098cc15e\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"dc584f15\",\n        \"seq\": 52\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"All done. Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"All done. Here's a summary of what was built:\\n\\n## ✅ Completed\\n\\n**4 channel service files created** in `src/infrastructure/channels/`:\\n- `twilio-sms.service.ts` — Twilio client wrapper with `send(phone, message)`\\n- `zalo-oa.service.ts` — Zalo OA v3 with token caching + `sendText(userId, message)`\\n- `fcm-push.service.ts` — Firebase Admin with lazy init, `sendToToken` + `sendToTopic`\\n- `notification-dispatcher.service.ts` — unified dispatcher routing to correct provider\\n\\n**Dependencies installed** via `yarn add twilio firebase-admin` + `yarn add -D @types/twilio`\\n\\n**`notify.service.ts` updated** — `send()` now:\\n1. Saves to DB (existing behavior)\\n2. Fetches user doc for channel recipients\\n3. Dispatches to SMS (`user.phone`), Zalo (`user.zalo_user_id`), FCM (`user.fcm_token`) as applicable\\n4. Falls back to `in_app` gracefully when no recipient is present\\n\\n**User model extended** — added `zalo_user_id?: string` and `fcm_token?: string` fields to `IUser` + schema\\n\\n**`.env.example` updated** — added `TWILIO_*`, `ZALO_*`, `FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT` placeholder keys\\n\\n**`yarn build` ✅ passes** (exit 0)\\n\\n**Commit:** `db6cc8f` — `feat(notification): add Twilio SMS, Zalo OA, and FCM push channel dispatchers`\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1776286098067,\n      \"responseId\": \"062f2c9358d9f2869b11c308b651c98a\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"ed132435\",\n        \"seq\": 54\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"truncated\": true,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": true,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 3191\n}"}],"details":{"sessionKey":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:7c788b0c-b9ba-4ade-ba13-92969a594785","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The build passes. Now let me commit the changes."},{"type":"text","text":"Build passes. Now commit:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nmrexx7g6wu8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be && git add src/infrastructure/channels/ src/infrastructure/database/models/user.model.ts src/application/services/notify.service.ts .env.example && git status --short"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776286090486,"responseId":"062f2c8c01609625ebe3502fc5297e39","__openclaw":{"id":"2ce70843","seq":50}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I should not commit `package.json` and `yarn.lock` since the task says to commit local only. Actually the task says \"DO NOT push to remote — commit local only\". So I can commit, just don't push. Let me commit everything including package.json and yarn.lock."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wprzyl8160up_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-drivi