{"type":"message","id":"99caa7ed","parentId":"6151b9b8","timestamp":"2026-04-15T20:50:55.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"BE .env.example is updated. Now let me commit the notificationService.ts change and then do a final status summary.\n\nLet me also add the channel badge to the announcement list items in the settings notification page, and also add the `sendNotification` import to the settings page.\n\nActually, the settings/notifications page doesn't need to call sendNotification directly - it uses createAnnouncement. The sendNotification is for sending to a single user, which might be used elsewhere.\n\nLet me now commit the notificationService.ts change and do a final summary.","thinkingSignature":"4b2bde6e0c9959f2a9b2aae6c0fed36572b757226644b1b02528027bf7ec9384"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0n8wsnm2ypgb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe && git add src/services/notificationService.ts && git commit -m \"feat(notificationService): add sendNotification API for single-user notification dispatch\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":247,"output":191,"cacheRead":97207,"cacheWrite":370,"totalTokens":98015,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776286249170,"responseId":"062f2d2a4ca91d9165111e76052e2aa1"}}
