{"type":"message","id":"22703ddd","parentId":"0abbec89","timestamp":"2026-04-16T02:11:34.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants to know what env variables are needed for the notification feature. Let me list them clearly.","thinkingSignature":"a8401f65f7415723e42a1beabfb9eb47a8aac05d9c45e5cb754cf240ae40db45"},{"type":"text","text":"**Env variables cần cho feature notification:**\n\n```env\n# Twilio SMS\nTWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_twilio_account_sid\nTWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_twilio_auth_token\nTWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890\n\n# Zalo OA\nZALO_APP_ID=your_zalo_app_id\nZALO_APP_SECRET=your_zalo_app_secret\nZALO_OA_ID=your_zalo_oa_id\n\n# Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM)\nFIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT={\"type\":\"service_account\",\"project_id\":\"...\",\"private_key\":\"...\",\"client_email\":\"...\"}\n```\n\nHiện tại trong `.env` chưa có — đang dùng placeholder. Khi Lead cung cấp keys, tôi update vào `.env` là notification sẽ hoạt động.\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":181,"output":217,"cacheRead":119586,"cacheWrite":589,"totalTokens":120573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776305486860,"responseId":"062f7850918f4378db0b851544638681"}}
