{"type":"message","id":"cd076aa6","parentId":"05b8a7d2","timestamp":"2026-04-16T02:23:17.082Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-16 02:23 UTC] Auto Reminder Cron what is a solution for best?"}],"timestamp":1776306197048}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f40f2b7","parentId":"cd076aa6","timestamp":"2026-04-16T02:23:51.079Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead is asking about the best solution for auto reminder cron - specifically for debt/tuition reminders. Let me think about the best approach for a teacher-only system.\n\nThe goal is to automatically remind students about outstanding tuition fees. Since this is teacher-only, the reminders should go TO students (via their contact channels), not to teachers.\n\nOptions:\n1. **Cron job on BE** - runs every day, checks overdue payments, sends notifications\n2. **Trigger-based** - fires when payment is overdue (more real-time)\n3. **Combined** - both\n\nFor best practice in a MongoDB/Node.js system:\n\n**Best approach: Hybrid**\n\n\nI'm weighing the trade-offs between a simple cron job that checks daily versus a real-time trigger that fires immediately when payments become overdue. The cron approach is easier to manage and less likely to have bugs, while the trigger-based approach catches issues faster but might miss if the system is down. I'll recommend a daily cron job with smart rules like sending reminders at 3, 7, and 14 days overdue, using different channels based on the student's preference, and logging everything in the system for the teacher to track.\n\nFor implementation, I'd structure it as a cron job running at 7 AM daily, query the database to find overdue payments, send notifications through in-app messaging and Zalo if available, use Twilio SMS as a fallback, and maintain a notification log so teachers can monitor what's been sent. The notification service would dispatch to whichever channel is most effective—Zalo for Vietnamese users with high open rates, SMS as a backup, and always in-app for record-keeping.\n\nThe system would send escalating reminders at 3, 7, and 14 days overdue with increasing urgency, and only send one notification per day per student to avoid spam.","thinkingSignature":"c876ac7981cd391256f3859a4527c61e259f053de802d9ae4b2de196cecf7a30"},{"type":"text","text":"\n### Auto Reminder Cron — Best Solution\n\n**Cách hoạt động:**\n\n```\nMỗi ngày 7:00 AM (UTC+7)\n    │\n    ▼\nTìm tất cả học viên có nợ học phí quá hạn\n    │\n    ▼\nVới mỗi học viên:\n  ├── 3 ngày quá hạn → Nhắc nhẹ (Zalo/SMS)\n  ├── 7 ngày quá hạn → Nhắc mạnh + thông báo giáo viên\n  └── 14 ngày quá hạn → Cảnh báo khẩn + chặn thi\n```\n\n### Notification Channels (ưu tiên)\n\n| Kênh | Chi phí | Tỉ lệ mở | Ghi chú |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **Zalo OA** | Miễn phí | 95% | Ưu tiên #1 |\n| **SMS (Twilio)** | ~350đ/tin | 90% | Backup |\n| **In-app** | Miễn phí | — | Lưu lịch sử |\n\n### Rules thông minh\n\n```\n✅ Gửi tối đa 1 lần/ngày/student (không spam)\n✅ Không gửi 21:00 - 08:00 (giờ nghỉ)\n✅ Template có {name}, {amount}, {due_date}\n✅ Log đầy đủ vào DB để teacher theo dõi\n✅ Có nút \"Đã thanh toán\" → teacher xác nhận\n```\n\n### Implementation\n\n```typescript\n// src/application/services/reminder.service.ts\n// Cron: every day at 7AM UTC+7\n// Queries: payment.overdue > 0 AND last_reminder_sent < today\n// Sends: Zalo → SMS → in_app (fallback chain)\n```\n\n### Teacher Dashboard (mới)\n\n```\n🔴 Nợ khẩn (14+ ngày): 5 học viên\n🟡 Nợ nhắc nhở (3-7 ngày): 12 học viên  \n🟢 Đã thanh toán hôm nay: 3 học viên\n```\n\n**Cần dùng chính sách gửi nào?** Zalo + SMS hay chỉ Zalo?\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":126,"output":933,"cacheRead":121248,"cacheWrite":1200,"totalTokens":123507,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776306197082,"responseId":"062f7b169ae7ab451592819bd7abdf54"}}
